text: Séamus Downey (born 13 June 1960) is a former cyclist from Northern Ireland. He competed in the individual road race event at the 1984 Summer Olympics for Ireland. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Cyclists from Northern Ireland Category:Olympic cyclists of Ireland Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
